{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<section class="hero">
	<img class="hero__image" src="{{ home.images.hero }}" alt="Global network visualization">
	<div class="hero__shade"></div>
	<div class="section-inner hero__content">
		<p class="eyebrow"><span></span> New Book - Available Now</p>
		<h1>Wild <span>Globalization</span></h1>
		<p class="hero__dek">A pan-historical exploration of the five wild forces - Ecology, Culture, Technology, Economy, and Governance - that drive and produce our hyper-globalizing civilization. It's wild.</p>
		<div class="actions">
			<a class="button" href="https://wildglobalization.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get Your Copy</a>
			<a class="button button--secondary" href="#book">Explore the Book</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="book">
	<div class="section-inner split">
		<div>
			<p class="section-label">The Book</p>
			<h2>Inside the <span>Black Box</span></h2>
			<p>Wild Globalization explores five primal forces-energies that drive and produce civilization. We may observe what comes out, but what happens inside that spontaneously evolving entanglement surpasses complete understanding. It's wild.</p>
			<a class="button" href="https://wildglobalization.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Order the Book</a>
		</div>
		<div class="book-cover">
			<img src="{{ home.images.book }}" alt="Wild Globalization book cover">
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="section-inner force-grid">
		{% for force in home.forces %}
			<article class="force-card">
				<div class="force-card__icon">{{ force.icon }}</div>
				<p class="force-card__label">{{ force.label }}</p>
				<h3>{{ force.heading }}</h3>
				<p>{{ force.body }}</p>
				<a href="{{ force.url }}">Explore this force <span aria-hidden="true">-&gt;</span></a>
			</article>
		{% endfor %}
	</div>
	<div class="section-inner">
		<figure class="image-banner">
			<img src="{{ home.images.port }}" alt="Massive shipping port at golden hour - the scale of global trade">
			<figcaption>"History's flow accelerates ahead of our practical and ethical responses."</figcaption>
		</figure>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section section--muted" id="about">
	<div class="section-inner section-heading">
		<p class="section-label">About the Work</p>
		<h2>More Provocateur <span>than Scholar</span></h2>
		<p>Wild Globalization doesn't offer easy ideology. It's a siren for critical thinking, dwelling in questions and wonderment rather than formal account, building its perspective from both the miracles and horrors of humankind.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="section-inner about-grid">
		{% for card in home.aboutCards %}
			<article>
				<div class="about-grid__icon">{{ card.icon }}</div>
				<h3>{{ card.title }}</h3>
				<p>{{ card.body }}</p>
			</article>
		{% endfor %}
	</div>
	<blockquote class="section-inner pullquote">
		<p>"Can we turn our incessantly creative-destructive and emerging hyper-tech nature back on itself to gain new comparative advantages? How can we, in the 21st century, regain practical advantage for our own - and the Earth's - precarious endurance?"</p>
		<cite>Wild Globalization</cite>
	</blockquote>
</section>

<section class="section" id="author">
	<div class="section-inner section-rule">
		<p class="section-label">The Author</p>
	</div>
	<div class="section-inner author-card">
		<div class="author-card__media">
			<img src="{{ home.images.author }}" alt="Author of Wild Globalization">
			<p><strong>The Wild Globalization Project</strong><span>Pan-historical analysis</span></p>
		</div>
		<div class="author-card__body">
			<h2>The Wild <span>Globalization</span><br>Project</h2>
			<p class="kicker">Author &amp; Thought Provocateur</p>
			<p>Wild Globalization speaks more like a <strong>provocateur than a scholar</strong>, a siren for critical thinking over ideology, dwelling in questions and wonderment rather than formal account.</p>
			<p>Drawing from paleoecology, economic history, technology theory, and governance across civilizations, the work builds its perspective simultaneously from the miracles and the horrors of the human story.</p>
			<p>At its core, it challenges all current governances, of every ideology, and their relentless advances into the externalities of massive public debt.</p>
			<div class="stats">
				<p><strong>5</strong><span>Wild Forces</span></p>
				<p><strong>250K</strong><span>Years of History</span></p>
				<p><strong>1</strong><span>Bold Thesis</span></p>
			</div>
			<div class="actions">
				<a class="button" href="https://wildglobalization.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit the Full Site</a>
				<a class="button button--secondary" href="#book">Explore the Forces</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
